rows.label: qst104006_msg001
rows.name:
Thank you for not only gathering the
medicine ingredients, but also for
saving me from that dangerous situation.

rows.label: qst104006_msg002
rows.name:
Now that we have what we came for,
we plan to return to Invidia.

rows.label: qst104006_msg003
rows.name:
We might be attacked again on the way
back, so we were thinking of hiring
a mercenary group to escort us...

rows.label: qst104006_msg004
rows.name:
Oh, no, we couldn't possibly
impose on you that much...

rows.label: qst104006_msg005
rows.name:
Really? In that case, we'll
humbly accept your offer.
We're in your hands.
